{
  "page": "Tourney for the completion of the Dragonpit",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>tourney for the completion of the Dragonpit</b> was held at <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> in mid <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_55_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">55&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#The_Joust\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Joust</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#The_Squire.27s_tourney\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Squire's tourney</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#The_Melee\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Melee</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Aftermath\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Aftermath</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_the_completion_of_the_Dragonpit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Manfryd_Redwyne\" title=\"Manfryd Redwyne\">Manfryd Redwyne</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_ships\" title=\"Master of ships\">master of ships</a>, proposed that the completion of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonpit\" title=\"Dragonpit\">Dragonpit</a> be celebrated with a great <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a>, to which King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>. Lists were raised in the fields west of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>'s city walls between the <a href=\"/index.php/Lion_Gate\" title=\"Lion Gate\">Lion Gate</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Gate\" title=\"King&#39;s Gate\">King's Gate</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After winning the squire's tourney, <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Redwyne\" title=\"Rickard Redwyne\">Rickard Redwyne</a> was knighted by Jaehaerys himself. The champion's laurels went to Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Dondarrion\" title=\"Simon Dondarrion\">Simon Dondarrion</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Blackhaven\" title=\"Blackhaven\">Blackhaven</a>, who won the love of the <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> and Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Targaryen\" title=\"Alysanne Targaryen\">Alysanne Targaryen</a> when he crowned Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen (daughter of Jaehaerys I)\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> as his <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_of_love_and_beauty\" title=\"Queen of love and beauty\">queen of love and beauty</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As no <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a> had been settled in the Dragonpit as yet, the huge building edifice was chosento host the tourney's grand melee, which involved seventy-seven knights divided into eleven teams. The participants began the melee on their <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">horses</a>, but continued fighting on foot with blunted weaponws after being unhorsed. When only one team remained, its members turned on one another until only a single champion remained. By melee's end, two men had been killed and more than twoscore were wounded. Queen Alysanne forbade her favorites, <a href=\"/index.php/Jonquil_Darke\" title=\"Jonquil Darke\">Jonquil Darke</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_the_Strummer\" title=\"Tom the Strummer\">Tom the Strummer</a>, from taking part in the melee.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Joust\">The Joust</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_the_completion_of_the_Dragonpit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Joust\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dondarrion\" title=\"House Dondarrion\"><img alt=\"House Dondarrion.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/32px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/48px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/House_Dondarrion.svg/64px-House_Dondarrion.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b>Champion</b>: Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Dondarrion\" title=\"Simon Dondarrion\">Simon Dondarrion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\"><img alt=\"House Redwyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/32px-House_Redwyne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/48px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/64px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b>Participant</b>: Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Redwyne\" title=\"Robert Redwyne\">Robert Redwyne</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span id=\"The_Squire's_tourney\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Squire.27s_tourney\">The Squire's tourney</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_the_completion_of_the_Dragonpit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Squire&#039;s tourney\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\"><img alt=\"House Redwyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/32px-House_Redwyne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/48px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0b/House_Redwyne.svg/64px-House_Redwyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b>Champion</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Rickard_Redwyne\" title=\"Rickard Redwyne\">Rickard Redwyne</a>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Melee\">The Melee</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_the_completion_of_the_Dragonpit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Melee\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Strong\" title=\"House Strong\"><img alt=\"House Strong.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/36/House_Strong.svg/32px-House_Strong.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/36/House_Strong.svg/48px-House_Strong.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/36/House_Strong.svg/64px-House_Strong.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b>Champion</b>: Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lucamore_Strong\" title=\"Lucamore Strong\">Lucamore Strong</a>\n</p><p><b>Known participants</b>:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Strong\" title=\"House Strong\"><img alt=\"House Strong.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/36/House_Strong.svg/32px-House_Strong.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/36/House_Strong.svg/48px-House_Strong.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/36/House_Strong.svg/64px-House_Strong.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lucamore_Strong\" title=\"Lucamore Strong\">Lucamore Strong</a></li>\n<li><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Willam_Stafford\" title=\"Willam Stafford\">Willam Stafford</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hogg\" title=\"House Hogg\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harys_Hogg\" title=\"Harys Hogg\">Harys Hogg</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bullock\" title=\"House Bullock\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Bullock\" title=\"Alyn Bullock\">Alyn Bullock</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/32px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/48px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/64px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Borys_Baratheon\" title=\"Borys Baratheon\">Borys Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/32px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/48px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/64px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Garon_Baratheon\" title=\"Garon Baratheon\">Garon Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/32px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/48px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/64px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnal_Baratheon\" title=\"Ronnal Baratheon\">Ronnal Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Guyle\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Guyle\">Guyle the Cunning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Reyne\" title=\"House Reyne\"><img alt=\"House Reyne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/House_Reyne.svg/32px-House_Reyne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3c/House_Reyne.svg/48px-House_Reyne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3c/House_Reyne.svg/64px-House_Reyne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alastor_Reyne\" title=\"Alastor Reyne\">Alastor Reyne</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Aftermath\">Aftermath</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_the_completion_of_the_Dragonpit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Aftermath\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Soon after the conclusion of the tourney, Queen Alysanne left King's Landing for <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>, there to await the birth of her child. Alysanne gave birth to Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Aemon</a> in late <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_55_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">55&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tourney_for_the_completion_of_the_Dragonpit&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabjaehaerys_and_alysanne_-_their_triumphs_and_tragedies.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Jaehaerys and Alysanne - Their Triumphs and Tragedies.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403172338\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.078 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.168 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 659/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 9130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3813/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1370/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2429/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.080/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.84 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  143.942      1 -total\n 55.62%   80.055     13 Template:Coa\n 26.54%   38.201      2 Template:Date\n 14.28%   20.554      5 Template